content:
Launch Model Manager from the Analytics panel in CRM Analytics Studio.

In the Analytics panel, click the Model Manager tab.
Review the statistics that summarize all deployed predictions definitions within your org.

Active/Total Models: Total number of deployed models that are active/inactive within the org.
Total Predictions: Total number of predictions made within the org for automated prediction fields.

COLUMN	DESCRIPTION
Prediction Definition: Name of the prediction definition.
Goal: Outcome variable for the prediction definition, and whether to minimize or maximize the outcome.
Active Models: Number of active models associated with the prediction definition.
Type: Regression, Binary Classification, or Multi-class Classification predictions.
Object: Salesforce object associated with the prediction definition.
Alerts: Number of data alerts associated with the prediction definition.
Data Refresh: Indicates whether scheduled automatic refresh is enabled for the prediction definition.
Last Update: Timestamp of the last update to the prediction definition.
title: Model Manager in Salesforce Analytics
